rows.label: tlk70000001_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Intelligence network and mobility of
Macmac is staggering. Some nightmare
where wings and feet sprout up!

rows.label: tlk70000001_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Like being watched wherever Morumo
goes! No means to escape! Has ears in
walls! In ceiling!

rows.label: tlk70000001_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Very distressing for Morumo.
Very, very! Started spending more
time with others.

rows.label: tlk70000001_05_msg0004
rows.name:
When on own, Morumo only worry
about Macmac. When in company, can
forget about Macmac.

rows.label: tlk70000001_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Then hear lots of stories from people
Morumo spend time with. Very big help!

rows.label: tlk70000001_05_msg0006
rows.name: Morumo want to help even more...

rows.label: tlk70000001_05_msg0007
rows.name:
Refuse to be beaten by Macmac.
Morumo sort things out and make
market bigger and better!
